{
  "page": "Amberly",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2;\">Amberly</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\nCastle</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlands</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Government</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogers\" title=\"House Rogers\">House Rogers</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Feudalism\" title=\"Feudalism\">Feudal lord</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Religion</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Named for</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Amber\" title=\"Amber\">Amber</a> (possibly)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Amberly</b> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Rogers\" title=\"House Rogers\">House Rogers</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>. According to semi-canon sources the castle might be named after large deposits of <a href=\"/index.php/Amber\" title=\"Amber\">amber</a> found in the ancient forests of the stormlands.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Amberly may be located in the <a href=\"/index.php/Rainwood\" title=\"Rainwood\">rainwood</a>, as that forest is known for its wealth in amber.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_the_men_of_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_the_men_of_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Amberly&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Amberly is named after <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roger_Zelazny\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Roger Zelazny\">Roger Zelazny</a>'s series <i><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Chronicles_of_Amber\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:The Chronicles of Amber\">The Chronicles of Amber</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Amberly&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. Heraldry: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/8/\">Houses from the Stormlands</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_the_men_of_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_stormlands:_the_men_of_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Stormlands: The Men of the Stormlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"